history.content:
DiversaTech is a student-run consultancy that works with companies such as Airbnb, LinkedIn, Slack, and Snackpass on impactful projects. From developing full-stack prototypes for high-impact startups to ideating new features for popular social media apps, our members continuously explore new skill sets and industry challenges.

At DiversaTech, we see tech differently: we believe that the most innovative solutions arise from diversity of thought, and strongly encourage people of all majors, interests, and backgrounds to apply. No technical or consulting experience required!

To learn more about us and our recruitment process, please visit our Facebook event at https://fb.me/e/1uaAz91RA or www.diversatech.org/apply. We look forward to meeting you!
history.subject: Join DiversaTech Consulting!
